---
title: Chermoula-Spiced Pork & Rainbow Slaw Tacos with Garlic Aioli & Roasted Almonds
description: Take taco night to the next level with the flavours of Turkey. Chermoula-spiced pork mince sits inside warm tortillas with a garlicky aioli and crunchy, fresh veggies for a flavour combination you didn’t know you were missing. It’s another taco-tastic dinner!

*We’ve replaced the radish in this recipe with sweetcorn due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
